Just moments from Jaipur’s Amber Fort, Anantara Jewel Bagh Jaipur invites you into a world of domed pavilions, Mughal-inspired gardens and tranquil courtyards.

Unwind with bespoke Ayurvedic spa treatments, explore the Pink City through curated cultural experiences or dine beneath the stars with flavours rooted in North Indian tradition.

Every detail is crafted to reflect the elegance of Rajasthan – and the serenity of Anantara.

Book your stay today at MinorHotels.com.

Just another morning at Anantara Jaipur—curtains dancing awake, beds fluffing into royalty, and robes waiting like loyal butlers.
The Royal Two-Bedroom Suite doesn’t just get ready… it makes an entrance. 

Rise and shine, the Presidential way.

#anantarajewelbaghjaipur #anantarajaipur #UnforgettableJourneys #anantara

From posing to pottery making, learning to make lost/forgotten dishes and even trying my hand at chakki ‘pisaoing’ the things I did at Anantara Jewel Bagh Jaipur! The luxury hotel also conducts an art walk that covers the history and technique behind the hotel’s artworks, including paintings, mirror mosaics, gold leafing and stone carvings. The best thing to do at @anantarajaipur? A candle lit dinner curated by executive chef Sunil Jajoria at the shimmering Sheesh Mahal!
